        <h1>Trachoma Photo Database</h1>
        <p class="lead">This database is the result of a collective effort by the trachoma community to support education and research efforts for trachoma elimination and long-term surveillance. </p>
        <p>It has been proposed that the use of photography and image grading can help us to overcome some of the trachoma diagnosis challenges we face. For the most recent progress report on this work please <a href="https://www.trachomacoalition.org/resources/use-photography-support-trachoma-grading-progress-report">click here</a>.</p>
        <p>This database was put together to create one acessible portal where images of the eye can be shared and accessed by stakeholders in the trachoma community for education and research.  Thank you for your support and for contributing to our efforts.</p>
        <p>Please note that Tropical Data administers this database on behalf of the trachoma community, with support from a Steering Committee. A list of members can be found <strong><a href="/documents/db-steeringcom.docx">here</a></strong>. If you have any questions, please contact <a href="mailto:admin@tropicaldata.org">admin@tropicaldata.org</a>. </p>
